{
  "stem": "7069.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But we noticed that they do not really go so much between our legs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so, as funny as-- terrible as this sounds, we figured that we'd pick the smaller tomatoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we had some kind of rag with a couple of safety pins where we'd maybe probably put four or five small tomatoes or more-- I don't know anymore the number-- made a roll out of it and rolled them up in this rag, put the safety pins on the end, and put them between our legs, tied them onto the pants inside.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we walked there-- a little gingerly, of course-- through the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Now, you see, when you are starving, and, and you have nothing of that kind ever in front of you, you don't really care much, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so, so--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, you do what you had to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is how we smuggled some of the tomatoes in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a wonderful thing. .",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at, at the moment, I didn't know anybody there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there were people of all--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there-- oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes you could see, when you walked down the street and somebody was not observant when an SS man came by and you didn't make-- get off the sidewalk or something like that.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although, you couldn't differentiate much between sidewalk and street because the streets were full with milling people, mostly old folks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The younger folks were sent to work, except maybe sometimes in late evening before curfew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I started-- we worked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I started soon to let it be known that I know how to design and build furniture.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was then commandeered into a workshop, where I was ordered to design and to build furniture.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
